public class FlowDrivenActivity.ActivityWorkGroup
extends Activity.ActivityWorkGroup
implements FlowDrivenActivityWorkGroup

A set of resources needed for carrying out an activity. A workgroup (WG) consists on a set of (resource type, #needed resources) pairs, a subflow, and the priority of the workgroup inside the activity.
